<TXT>US manufactured ballasts shall not be mixed with Japan manufactured ballasts.  The Contractor shall segregate and palletize US manufactured ballasts 
separately from Japan manufactured ballasts<TAI OPT="MARINE CORPS IN OKINAWA"> at the point of generation for subsequent turn in to the MCB Butler EST (HW/PCB Program Manager, 098-970-3139 
