<SPT outline="3.8.2"><TTL>For Japan Manufactured Ballasts</TTL><BRK />
<BRK />
<TXT>The Contractor shall carefully examine the ballast to identify the manufacturer name and year made.  Consult with the manufacturer to identify 
any presence of PCBs.  If absence of PCB cannot be confirmed, assume and treat the ballast as a PCB item.</TXT><BRK />
